Because I am getting some new followers thanks to @bronzeagemantis (PBUH) I am going to make a short thread where I will reveal some of my surface-level gym BICEPS secrets... Beware, most were shared with me by European International champions, old coaches...

First is the biceps... Most people think they are doing a good job of training biceps by doing regular curls once weekly... Biceps are one of the FASTEST RECOVERING muscles, you should be training them EVERY OTHER DAY.
For biceps to be pronounced, it is important to also train your BRACHIALIS, Best way to do it to do CROSSOVER HAMMER CURLS, they will hit your biceps AND brachialis, making it pop...
Next trick is a bit more advanced... When doing one arm dumbbell curls TOUCH your biceps with your finger of the other hand... this improves MIND-MUSCLE connection.
ARNOLD said that when doing BICEPS CURLS he imagined his biceps GETTING AS BIG AS THE ROOM, EXPANDING WITH EVERY REP. Try to do that, FORCE your mind to think about the muscle and feel it...
